                            <comment id="14226589" author="philipthompson" created="Wed, 26 Nov 2014 18:32:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I applied your patch to CCM.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14234334" author="jmckenzie" created="Thu, 4 Dec 2014 16:34:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1, though we might want to add in a test for sstablesplit w/abort() path instead of finish() just to be safe.  abort() code looks like it shouldn&apos;t give us any problems while isOffline but may as well while we&apos;re here.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
